window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The time for liberation has come.</b></p> <p>With the Republic's army now on their side, Alexandra and her allies can finally look northâ€”towards the embattled Asarian Kingdom, deep in the throes of civil war, as the slavers of Sunrise besiege its capital.</p> <p>They must liberate Darthar, the jewel of the wastelands, if they are to restore the connection Rebirth had with the Duchy of Sarth and what remains of the kingdom beyond.</p> <p>Meanwhile, ever so slowly, the world marches towards annihilation, as conspiracies millennia in the making reach their crescendo, and the entire planet teeters on the brink.</p>"; 
